0.0.5
=====

- Add support for title and descriptions in Command help
- Add support for adding title/description by writing docstrings on a wrapped
  handler.
- Refactored methods to have better, more intuitive naming
- Add lots of documentation and docstrings


0.0.1
=====

Initial migration of the Clams library from the
[unb-cli](https://bitbucket.org/unbsolutions/unb-cli) project.
